"""
    Check that a record returns the correct success rate.
    """
record = Record()
assert record.success_rate() == 0
record.successes = 5
record.fails = 5
assert record.success_rate() == 50
record.fails = 0
assert record.success_rate() == 100
record.fails = 5
record.successes = 0
assert record.success_rate() == 0
